# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo

# Generated search index. The metadata JSON has a committed empty placeholder
# (src/data/asset-index.json) that `npm run build:index` overwrites; the binary
# vector blob is generated and never committed. In production both files are
# produced by the reindex cron job, uploaded to R2, and fetched at build time
# (npm run fetch:index) — so neither belongs in git.
/src/data/asset-index.vec.bin
